(16, 1, '2020-02-12 01:25:46', '2020-02-12 01:25:46', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Save On Clouds can send notifications to Google Chat Rooms via Webhooks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In order to receive notifications, firstly you need to create a room.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":11,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once the room is created, make sure you are in the room. Then expand the drop-down menu on the top of the screen and click on \"Configure Webhooks\" option.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":13,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/image-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-13\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Provide a name and click on Save.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":14,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/image-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-14\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once you click on the Save button, Google Chat will provide you with a Webhook address. This URL is what you need to place in Save On Clouds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":15,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/image-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-15\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Copy the provided link/URL to the clipboard, and go back to your profile page Save On Clouds. In the Notifications tab, add a Google Chat notification channel and paste the link in the Address box.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Integration with Google Chat Hangout', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-02-12 01:25:46', '2020-02-12 01:25:46', '', 10, 'https://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/10-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(17, 1, '2020-04-26 20:46:37', '2020-04-26 20:46:37', '<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":120,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://www.stickpng.com/assets/images/5cb480cd5f1b6d3fbadece79.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"120\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Save On Clouds can send notifications to Slack via Webhooks. Webhooks are configured at the \"Channel\" level in Slack.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Create a room and call it \"Save On Clouds\". Then make sure you are inside the Channel.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When in the Channel, click on the settings icon, which is a cog, and from the drop-down menu choose Add an app.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":18,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/image-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-18\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This will bring up the App Directory where you can search for Incoming Webhooks app.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Add this app and follow the instructions to complete the app installations. Once the app is installed you will see \"Webhook Url\" section in the Incoming Webhook configuration page. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":19,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/image-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Copy this URL to the clipboard and go back to Save On Clouds. Go to your profile page and find the Notifications tab.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Add a Slack notification channel, and paste the copied URL in the Address box.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Integration with Slack', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'integration-with-slack', '', '', '2020-04-26 20:46:37', '2020-04-26 20:46:37', '', 0, 'http://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/?p=17', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(18, 1, '2020-02-12 01:35:35', '2020-02-12 01:35:35', '', 'image-8', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'image-8', '', '', '2020-02-12 01:35:35', '2020-02-12 01:35:35', '', 17, 'http://saveoncloudsblog.cloud/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/image-8.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
