(111, 1, '2020-04-18 11:02:39', '2020-04-18 11:02:39', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We invite you to watch our explainer video before you read the rest of this article.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:cover {\"url\":\"http://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/save_on_clouds.mp4\",\"id\":109,\"backgroundType\":\"video\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim\"><video class=\"wp-block-cover__video-background\" autoplay muted loop src=\"http://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/save_on_clouds.mp4\"></video><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"placeholder\":\"Write title…\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\">About Save On Clouds</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->', 'About Save On Clouds', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '107-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-04-18 11:02:39', '2020-04-18 11:02:39', '', 107, 'https://info.saveonclouds.com/107-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(112, 1, '2020-04-18 11:11:17', '2020-04-18 11:11:17', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We invite you to watch our explainer video before you read the rest of this article.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/4R6SRpR8tHg\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/4R6SRpR8tHg\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Save On Clouds', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '107-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-04-18 11:11:17', '2020-04-18 11:11:17', '', 107, 'https://info.saveonclouds.com/107-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(113, 1, '2020-04-26 23:35:54', '2020-04-26 23:35:54', '<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-rounded\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://banner2.cleanpng.com/20180506/vhw/kisspng-webhook-slack-application-programming-interface-5aef6ba8145e52.2061982515256401040834.jpg\" alt=\"Pink Circle png download - 1600*1600 - Free Transparent Webhook ...\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Generic Web-Hook integration will enable you to send notifications to virtually unlimited number and types of applications, as long as they support incoming web hooks. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using Web Hooks you can also initiate automation processes using third-party systems such as <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://zapier.com\" target=\"_blank\">Zapier</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All Web Hooks are accessible via a Service URL. This is how applications such as Slack, MS Teams and Google Hangouts are able to receive notifications from Save On Clouds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To integrate with a generic Web Hook, please refer to the documentation of your specific application and find out how Incoming Web-hooks are configured.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once the incoming webhook is configured in your applciation, head back to Save On Clouds and add a new notification channel of type \"WebHook\". Then put your Webhook Url in the Endpoint box and your channels.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No further configuration is required apart from deciding what kinds of alerts you would like to receive. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Integration with Generic Web Hook', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'integration-with-microsoft-teams', '', '', '2020-04-27 00:09:35', '2020-04-27 00:09:35', '', 0, 'http://info.saveonclouds.com/?p=113', 0, 'post', '', 0),
