(123, 1, '2020-04-26 23:35:54', '2020-04-26 23:35:54', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Integration with Microsoft Team is quite straightforward and it starts with creating a team and a channel for the team. For example, you can have a team called \"Notifications\" and a channel underneath that called \"Genera\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":114,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image-40.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-114\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once the channel is created, you will need to add the WebHook app to your channel. You do this by clicking on the \"Apps\" item in the main menu (left-side pane).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":115,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image-41.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-115\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Search for \"Webhook\", and find the \"Incoming Webhook\" app.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":116,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image-42-1024x402.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-116\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Click on the app and wait until the configuration window opens. Then click on \"Add to a team\" button.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":117,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image-43.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-117\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the search box, look  up your Team\'s name (not your channel\'s name):</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":118,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image-44-1024x578.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-118\"/><figcaption>Once the Team is chosen, click on \"Setup a connector\" button:<br></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":119,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image-45.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-119\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Configure the Incoming Webhook connector and provide a name (and optionally an image):</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":121,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image-47-965x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-121\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Then scroll down and click on the \"Create\" button.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wait for a few seconds until the webhook address appears. Copy the link into the Clipboard.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":122,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://info.saveonclouds.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image-48.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-122\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now go back to the \"Notifications\" page in your Save On Clouds portal, then add on \"Microsoft Teams\" button. Paste the link in the \"Address\" box and click on save button. You are all set!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Integration with Microsoft Teams', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '113-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-04-26 23:35:54', '2020-04-26 23:35:54', '', 113, 'https://info.saveonclouds.com/113-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
